(:action mine-potatoes
        :parameters (?target - object ?targetinv - inventory ?t - tile ?tool - object ?x - object ?toolinv - inventory)

        :precondition (and 
		(agent-at ?t)
		(object-at ?x ?t)
		(object-of-type ?x PotatoPlant)
		(inventory-holding ?toolinv ?tool)
